---
title: Toasted Rice and Shrimp Bowl with Bell Peppers and Corn
description: Oh rice, how we adore you. You pair well with pretty much every veggie and spice we can think of, add a satisfying heartiness to any meal, and—most importantly—are loved by even the pickiest eaters. So we’re pretty sure that you’ll take to the colorful veggies, flavorful shrimp, and dashes of juicy lime that fill out this dish like they’re your dearest pals, making for a fried rice friendship that’s built on harmony.
